preface
a
rdfs:Class
rdfs:comment
Text expression preceding a literary expression, usually written by the (main) author, stating the origin of the literary expression, its scope, purpose, plan, and intended audience, and including any afterthoughts and acknowledgments of assistance; possibly rewritten to alert the reader to changes in the literary expression.
rdfs:isDefinedBy
http://www.e-editiones.ch/ ontology/ literature#
rdfs:seeAlso
https://www.abc-clio.com/ ODLIS/ odlis f.aspx
